      "content": "hey i'm looking at our quarterly reports for the electronics warehouse and our shrinkage numbers are way higher than usual. i need to figure out how this unexpected loss is going to mess with our inventory turnover ratio. can you help me with the math on how to factor shrinkage into the turnover calculation?",
